{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1775839108362,"sessionID":"ses_287bdecbbffeOQyRZQ8xaEsMA4","part":{"id":"prt_d784257f0001gnZgtT1vrZHSBd","messageID":"msg_d784234f9001nX2In3nlfUiwQh","sessionID":"ses_287bdecbbffeOQyRZQ8xaEsMA4","type":"tool","tool":"read","callID":"toolu_tool-4ebea4b356604943a35efa885554105d","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md"},"output":"<path>/home/dsj/benchmark/workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md</path>\n<type>file</type>\n<content>\n1: # AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n2: \n3: ## Overview\n4: \n5: | Item | Value |\n6: |------|-------|\n7: | AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n8: | Module | `pkg/apis` |\n9: | Language | Go |\n10: | Size | S |\n11: | Stage | ST-1 |\n12: \n13: 定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n14: \n15: ## Design\n16: \n17: ### Architecture\n18: \n19: CRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n20: - 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema\n21: - 类型定义与 DeepCopy 代码分离，由 controller-gen 自动生成\n22: - 支持 status subresource，用于控制器更新资源状态\n23: - Namespaced scope，每个命名空间内独立管理运行时实例\n24: \n25: ### Dependencies\n26: \n27: | Package | Purpose |\n28: |---------|---------|\n29: | `k8s.io/api/core/v1` | PodSpec、EnvVar、PullPolicy、ResourceRequirements 等 |\n30: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/apis/meta/v1` | TypeMeta、ObjectMeta、Condition、Duration |\n31: | `k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema` | GroupVersion、GroupVersionResource |\n32: \n33: ### Controller-gen Markers\n34: \n35: | Marker | Applied to | Purpose |\n36: |--------|------------|---------|\n37: | `+kubebuilder:object:root=true` | Main type + List type | 注册到 Scheme |\n38: | `+kubebuilder:subresource:status` | Main type | 启用 status subresource |\n39: | `+kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced` | Main type | 命名空间级别资源 |\n40: | `+kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\"` | Main type | kubectl 输出列 |\n41: | `+genclient` | Main type | 生成 typed client |\n42: | `+k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=...` | Main type + List type | DeepCopy 接口 |\n43: \n44: ## Data Structures\n45: \n46: ### groupversion_info.go\n47: \n48: ```go\n49: // +groupName=runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\n50: package v1alpha1\n51: \n52: import \"k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime/schema\"\n53: \n54: var (\n55:     GroupVersion = schema.GroupVersion{\n56:         Group:   \"runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh\",\n57:         Version: \"v1alpha1\",\n58:     }\n59:     SchemeBuilder = &scheme.Builder{GroupVersion: GroupVersion}\n60:     AddToScheme   = SchemeBuilder.AddToScheme\n61: )\n62: ```\n63: \n64: ### register.go\n65: \n66: ```go\n67: var (\n68:     CodeInterpreterKind             = \"CodeInterpreter\"\n69:     CodeInterpreterGroupKind        = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n70:     CodeInterpreterListKind         = \"CodeInterpreterList\"\n71:     CodeInterpreterGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"CodeInterpreter\")\n72: \n73:     AgentRuntimeKind             = \"AgentRuntime\"\n74:     AgentRuntimeListKind         = \"AgentRuntimeList\"\n75:     AgentRuntimeGroupVersionKind = GroupVersion.WithKind(\"AgentRuntime\")\n76: )\n77: \n78: var SchemeGroupVersion = GroupVersion\n79: \n80: func Resource(resource string) schema.GroupVersionResource {\n81:     return GroupVersion.WithResource(resource)\n82: }\n83: ```\n84: \n85: ### AgentRuntime Types\n86: \n87: ```go\n88: // +genclient\n89: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n90: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n91: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n92: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n93: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n94: type AgentRuntime struct {\n95:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n96:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n97:     Spec   AgentRuntimeSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n98:     Status AgentRuntimeStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n99: }\n100: \n101: type AgentRuntimeSpec struct {\n102:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n103:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"targetPort\"`\n104:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n105:     Template *SandboxTemplate `json:\"podTemplate\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,opt,name=podTemplate\"`\n106:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n107:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n108:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,opt,name=sessionTimeout\"`\n109:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n110:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n111:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=maxSessionDuration\"`\n112: }\n113: \n114: type AgentRuntimeStatus struct {\n115:     // +optional\n116:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n117: }\n118: \n119: type SandboxTemplate struct {\n120:     // +optional\n121:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,1,rep,name=labels\"`\n122:     // +optional\n123:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\" protobuf:\"bytes,2,rep,name=annotations\"`\n124:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n125:     Spec corev1.PodSpec `json:\"spec\" protobuf:\"bytes,3,opt,name=spec\"`\n126: }\n127: \n128: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n129: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n130: type AgentRuntimeList struct {\n131:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n132:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n133:     Items           []AgentRuntime `json:\"items\"`\n134: }\n135: ```\n136: \n137: ### CodeInterpreter Types\n138: \n139: ```go\n140: // +genclient\n141: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n142: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n143: // +kubebuilder:subresource:status\n144: // +kubebuilder:resource:scope=Namespaced\n145: // +kubebuilder:printcolumn:name=\"Age\",type=\"date\",JSONPath=\".metadata.creationTimestamp\"\n146: type CodeInterpreter struct {\n147:     metav1.TypeMeta   `json:\",inline\"`\n148:     metav1.ObjectMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n149:     Spec   CodeInterpreterSpec   `json:\"spec\"`\n150:     Status CodeInterpreterStatus `json:\"status,omitempty\"`\n151: }\n152: \n153: type CodeInterpreterSpec struct {\n154:     // +optional\n155:     Ports []TargetPort `json:\"ports,omitempty\"`\n156:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Required\n157:     Template *CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate `json:\"template\"`\n158:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"15m\"\n159:     SessionTimeout *metav1.Duration `json:\"sessionTimeout,omitempty\"`\n160:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"8h\"\n161:     MaxSessionDuration *metav1.Duration `json:\"maxSessionDuration,omitempty\"`\n162:     // +optional\n163:     WarmPoolSize *int32 `json:\"warmPoolSize,omitempty\"`\n164:     // +kubebuilder:default=\"picod\"\n165:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=picod;none\n166:     // +optional\n167:     AuthMode AuthModeType `json:\"authMode,omitempty\"`\n168: }\n169: \n170: type CodeInterpreterStatus struct {\n171:     // +optional\n172:     Conditions []metav1.Condition `json:\"conditions,omitempty\"`\n173:     // +optional\n174:     Ready bool `json:\"ready,omitempty\"`\n175: }\n176: \n177: type CodeInterpreterSandboxTemplate struct {\n178:     // +optional\n179:     Labels map[string]string `json:\"labels,omitempty\"`\n180:     // +optional\n181:     Annotations map[string]string `json:\"annotations,omitempty\"`\n182:     // +optional\n183:     RuntimeClassName *string `json:\"runtimeClassName,omitempty\"`\n184:     Image string `json:\"image,omitempty\"`\n185:     // +optional\n186:     ImagePullPolicy corev1.PullPolicy `json:\"imagePullPolicy,omitempty\"`\n187:     // +optional\n188:     // +patchMergeKey=name\n189:     // +patchStrategy=merge\n190:     // +listType=map\n191:     // +listMapKey=name\n192:     ImagePullSecrets []corev1.LocalObjectReference `json:\"imagePullSecrets,omitempty\"`\n193:     // +optional\n194:     Environment []corev1.EnvVar `json:\"environment,omitempty\"`\n195:     // +optional\n196:     // +listType=atomic\n197:     Command []string `json:\"command,omitempty\"`\n198:     // +optional\n199:     Args []string `json:\"args,omitempty\"`\n200:     // +optional\n201:     Resources corev1.ResourceRequirements `json:\"resources,omitempty\"`\n202: }\n203: \n204: // +k8s:deepcopy-gen:interfaces=k8s.io/apimachinery/pkg/runtime.Object\n205: // +kubebuilder:object:root=true\n206: type CodeInterpreterList struct {\n207:     metav1.TypeMeta `json:\",inline\"`\n208:     metav1.ListMeta `json:\"metadata,omitempty\"`\n209:     Items           []CodeInterpreter `json:\"items\"`\n210: }\n211: ```\n212: \n213: ### Shared Types\n214: \n215: ```go\n216: type TargetPort struct {\n217:     // +optional\n218:     PathPrefix string `json:\"pathPrefix,omitempty\"`\n219:     // +optional\n220:     Name string `json:\"name,omitempty\"`\n221:     Port uint32 `json:\"port\"`\n222:     // +kubebuilder:default=HTTP\n223:     // +kubebuilder:validation:Enum=HTTP;HTTPS;\n224:     Protocol ProtocolType `json:\"protocol\"`\n225: }\n226: \n227: type AuthModeType string\n228: \n229: const (\n230:     AuthModePicoD AuthModeType = \"picod\"\n231:     AuthModeNone  AuthModeType = \"none\"\n232: )\n233: \n234: type ProtocolType string\n235: \n236: const (\n237:     ProtocolTypeHTTP  ProtocolType = \"HTTP\"\n238:     ProtocolTypeHTTPS ProtocolType = \"HTTPS\"\n239: )\n240: ```\n241: \n242: ## API Schema\n243: \n244: ### CRD OpenAPI Constraints\n245: \n246: | Resource | Required Spec Fields |\n247: |----------|----------------------|\n248: | AgentRuntime | `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration` |\n249: | CodeInterpreter | `template` |\n250: \n251: ### Defaults\n252: \n253: | Field | Default Value |\n254: |-------|---------------|\n255: | `sessionTimeout` | `15m` |\n256: | `maxSessionDuration` | `8h` |\n257: | `authMode` | `picod` |\n258: | `targetPort[].protocol` | `HTTP` |\n259: \n260: ### Enums\n261: \n262: | Field | Allowed Values |\n263: |-------|----------------|\n264: | `authMode` | `picod`, `none` |\n265: | `protocol` | `HTTP`, `HTTPS` |\n266: \n267: ### REST Resource Plurals\n268: \n269: | Kind | Plural |\n270: |------|--------|\n271: | AgentRuntime | `agentruntimes` |\n272: | CodeInterpreter | `codeinterpreters` |\n273: \n274: ### Printer Columns\n275: \n276: | Name | Type | JSONPath |\n277: |------|------|----------|\n278: | Age | date | `.metadata.creationTimestamp` |\n279: \n280: ## Error Handling\n281: \n282: - 无 spec 必填字段时，API server 拒绝创建请求（validation error）\n283: - 无效 enum 值时，API server 返回 validation error\n284: - Duration 格式错误时，使用 Go `metav1.Duration` 解析失败抛出错误\n285: \n286: ## Testing Strategy\n287: \n288: ### Unit Tests\n289: \n290: | Test Category | Coverage |\n291: |---------------|----------|\n292: | DeepCopy generation | 确保 DeepCopy 方法正确复制所有字段（deep vs shallow） |\n293: | Default values | 验证 kubebuilder 默认值标记生效 |\n294: | Enum validation | 测试所有允许值及无效值 |\n295: | JSON serialization | 验证 JSON tag 正确映射 |\n296: \n297: ### Integration Tests\n298: \n299: - CRD 安装验证：确保 `make gen-crd` 生成的 YAML 可被 k8s API server 接受\n300: - Client-go 生成验证：`make gen-client` 生成的 client/informer/lister 可正常使用\n301: \n302: ### Test File Structure\n303: \n304: ```\n305: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n306:   types_test.go       — DeepCopy、默认值、JSON 序列化测试\n307: ```\n308: \n309: ### Test Utilities\n310: \n311: 使用 `sigs.k8s.io/controller-runtime/pkg/webhook` 进行 validation 测试（如需 webhook）。\n312: \n313: ## File Structure\n314: \n315: ```\n316: pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/\n317:   groupversion_info.go   — GroupVersion 定义、SchemeBuilder\n318:   register.go            — Kind constants、Resource helper\n319:   agentruntime_types.go  — AgentRuntime、AgentRuntimeList、SandboxTemplate\n320:   codeinterpreter_types.go — CodeInterpreter、CodeInterpreterList、共享类型\n321:   doc.go                 — 包文档（可选）\n322: \n323: client-go/                — 由 make gen-client 生成\n324:   clientset/\n325:   informers/\n326:   listers/\n327: ```\n328: \n329: ## Generation Commands\n330: \n331: | Command | Output |\n332: |---------|--------|\n333: | `make generate` | DeepCopy 代码 + CRD YAML（`manifests/charts/base/crds/`） |\n334: | `make gen-client` | client-go（clientset、informers、listers） |\n335: | `make gen-all` | 以上全部 |\n336: \n337: ## Open Questions\n338: \n339: - [已解决] 默认值由 kubebuilder markers 定义\n340: - [已解决] Status 字段包含 `Conditions`（通用）和 `Ready`（CodeInterpreter）\n341: - 是否需要添加 additionalPrinterColumns（如 Ready 状态）？\n342: - 是否需要 webhook 进行更复杂验证？\n343: \n344: ## References\n345: \n346: - Source: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n347: - client-go: `/tmp/agentcube-ref/client-go/`\n348: - controller-tools version: `v0.17.2`\n\n(End of file - total 348 lines)\n</content>","metadata":{"preview":"# AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 Design\n\n## Overview\n\n| Item | Value |\n|------|-------|\n| AR | AR-001 — CRD AgentRuntime 类型定义 |\n| Module | `pkg/apis` |\n| Language | Go |\n| Size | S |\n| Stage | ST-1 |\n\n定义 AgentRuntime 和 CodeInterpreter CRD 的 Go 类型结构，作为 agentcube 的核心数据模型。API group: `runtime.agentcube.volcano.sh/v1alpha1`。\n\n## Design\n\n### Architecture\n\nCRD 类型定义遵循 Kubernetes API conventions：\n- 使用 `kubebuilder` markers 生成 OpenAPI schema","truncated":false,"loaded":[]},"title":"workspaces/v5.1/opencode-cli_bailian-coding-plan-glm-5_20260410T163124Z/changes/AR-001/design.md","time":{"start":1775839108338,"end":1775839108360}}}}
