erList` struct with appropriate markers\n  - Verify: `go build ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/`\n\n### Phase 3: Code Generation\n\n- [ ] **T3.1** Run `controller-gen object paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...` to generate DeepCopy methods\n  - Verify: `zz_generated.deepcopy.go` file created\n  - Verify: All types implement `runtime.Object` interface\n\n- [ ] **T3.2** Run `controller-gen crd paths=./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... output:crd:dir=manifests/charts/base/crds`\n  - Verify: CRD YAML files generated for `agentruntimes` and `codeinterpreters`\n\n- [ ] **T3.3** Run `client-gen` to generate client-go code\n  - Output to `client-go/` directory\n  - Verify: `clientset/`, `informers/`, `listers/` directories created\n\n### Phase 4: Unit Tests\n\n- [ ] **T4.1** Create `pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/types_test.go`\n  - Test DeepCopy for `AgentRuntime` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n  - Test DeepCopy for `CodeInterpreter` (verify deep copy of all fields)\n  - Test default values applied correctly (`sessionTimeout=15m`, `maxSessionDuration=8h`, `authMode=picod`)\n  - Test enum validation for `AuthModeType` and `ProtocolType`\n  - Test JSON serialization/deserialization for all types\n  - Verify: `go test ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/... -v`\n\n### Phase 5: Validation & Quality\n\n- [ ] **T5.1** Run `go vet ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n  - Fix any issues reported\n\n- [ ] **T5.2** Run `golangci-lint run ./pkg/apis/runtime/v1alpha1/...`\n  - Fix any linting issues\n\n- [ ] **T5.3** Verify JSON tags use camelCase for all struct fields\n  - Check: `targetPort`, `podTemplate`, `sessionTimeout`, `maxSessionDuration`\n  - Check: `pathPrefix`, `imagePullPolicy`, `imagePullSecrets`\n\n- [ **T5.4** Verify Kubernetes API conventions compliance\n  - All required fields have `+kubebuilder:validation:Required` marker\n  - Optional fields have `+optional` marker\n  - Default values specified with `+kubebuilder:default=...`\n\n### Phase 6: Documentation\n\n- [ ] **T6.1** Add godoc 